reviewText: I was disappinted by the first selection, Belshazzar's Feast, although it was certainly well done. Then Bryn Terfel's wonderful performance of Rule Brittania seemed to have been cut - it didn't show the conductor's remark after he was done, asking the audience shall we do that again?  I have the performance on Youtube, which is much better.As for the rest, I haven't listened to all of it yet.
